1
00:00:08,166 --> 00:00:10,125
EN NETFLIX-SERIE

2
00:00:55,125 --> 00:00:55,958
Absolut.

3
00:00:58,125 --> 00:00:59,166
- Ja?
- Ja.

4
00:00:59,250 --> 00:01:00,291
- Ja?
- Ja.

5
00:01:13,250 --> 00:01:14,375
Ja, precis så där...

6
00:01:17,708 --> 00:01:18,541
Kolla det här!

7
00:01:22,333 --> 00:01:25,291
Älskling! Herregud!

8
00:01:28,208 --> 00:01:30,291
Nej!

9
00:01:48,458 --> 00:01:52,375
Jag hittade nåt billigare,
men jag vet inte om jag vill bo där.

10
00:01:53,083 --> 00:01:54,750
Usch, han får du ta hand om!

11
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:07,750
Vad i helvete?

12
00:02:13,291 --> 00:02:14,500
AKUTMOTTAGNING

13
00:02:44,625 --> 00:02:45,750
FÖRSTA MÅLET VINNER

14
00:02:56,791 --> 00:02:59,000
Nej! Vänta med att skjuta!

15
00:03:05,083 --> 00:03:06,750
Ta kål på dem!

16
00:03:06,833 --> 00:03:08,791
- Skjut dem i kuken!
- Jävla skit!

17
00:03:12,916 --> 00:03:15,541
HJÄLP

18
00:03:18,333 --> 00:03:21,583
Hallå? Zombier? Inte i vårt land!

19
00:03:44,916 --> 00:03:49,791
HELVETET

20
00:04:22,291 --> 00:04:24,166
Jösses! Vad ska vi ta oss till?

21
00:04:26,541 --> 00:04:27,666
Skit samma!

22
00:04:28,875 --> 00:04:30,458
Sug på de här!

23
00:05:50,458 --> 00:05:52,333
Undertexter: Mats Nilsson

